summary: Completed comprehensive frontend testing of Fire Launch marketing website. All core functionality, design elements, and user interactions working correctly.
passed_tests: Homepage loads correctly with hero section and red underline animation
Sticky navigation with Book Free Call button functional
Services section displays all 5 service cards correctly
Pricing section shows 3 tiers with correct amounts (£799, £999, £1,500)
Growth Launch pricing card properly highlighted with red border and 'Most Popular' badge
Testimonials section displays 2 testimonial cards with 5-star ratings
All Calendly links (11 total) work correctly and open in new tabs
Demo Stores page loads with all 6 store cards and valid images
Navigation between homepage and demo stores works seamlessly
Mobile responsiveness: menu button, mobile CTA bar, and responsive design functional
Footer displays correctly with proper links and email contact
Color scheme matches Fire Launch branding (Crimson Flame #D92D20)
Typography uses correct fonts (Space Grotesk for headings, Inter for body)
Scroll behavior and sticky navigation shadow effect working
